naan sigappu manithan ( english : i am i ) is a 2014 indian tamil-language action thriller film written and directed by s. v. leone . the film features newcomer nikki galrani in the lead roles , with music composed by yuvan shankar raja and cinematography handled by s. v. kathir . the film features music composed by yuvan shankar raja and cinematography handled by s. a. rajkumar . the film was produced by v. v. satyanarayana under the banner of &lt;unk&gt; films . the film was released on 1 january 2014 . the film received positive reviews from critics .